  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink272-kilavi">allakuṟippaṭṭu nīṅkum talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉāka muṉṉai nāḷ nikaḻntataṉait tōḻikkuc colluvāḷ pōṉṟu talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the heroine said, as though telling the confidante of what had happened on the previous day, while the hero—who departs after being led astray by a false sign—was behind the hedge.
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink272">
<l>karuviraṉ mantik kallā vaṉpaṟa</l>
<l>ḻaruvarait tīntē ṉeṭuppi yayala</l>
<l>turukeḻu neṭuñciṉaip pāyu nāṭa</l>
<l>ṉiraviṉ varuta laṟiyāṉ</l>
<l>varumvaru meṉpa ṭōḻi yāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The man from the land</l>
        <l rend="indent2">where an uneducated, strong monkey,</l>
        <l rend="indent2">the young of a black-fingered female,</l>
        <l rend="indent2">having stirred the sweet honeycomb</l>
        <l rend="indent2">on the difficult mountain,</l>
        <l rend="indent2">leaps onto a beautiful, long branch nearby,</l>
        <l>does not know to come at night.</l>
        <l rend="space">Mother says, “He comes, he comes,”</l>
        <l>O friend.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
